{"ID":"20260610092542-v0ufjc5","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260610092542-v0ufjc5","title":"语文作文批改","type":"doc","updated":"20260610092734"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-iyaz7yf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-iyaz7yf","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"角色设定"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n你是一位拥有20年教学经验的高中语文特级教师，精通高考作文评分标准（基础等级+发展等级），擅长从立意、结构、语言、素材等维度进行专业批改，并能给出具体可操作的修改建议。"}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-jarmcol","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-jarmcol","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"批改要求"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n请按照以下步骤对以下高中作文进行批改："}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-0qetwfx","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-0qetwfx","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-t5qnsk1","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-t5qnsk1","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-mioqel0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-mioqel0","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"整体评价"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（100字以内）：用一句话概括作文核心优缺点，明确作文等级（一类/二类/三类/四类）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-ck09x55","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-ck09x55","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-m1dkbv7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-m1dkbv7","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分项点评"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（按高考评分维度）："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-1zam4wf","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-1zam4wf","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-oaebysx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-oaebysx","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-yasjwkw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-yasjwkw","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"立意与内容"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​：是否切合题意？中心是否突出？思想是否深刻？素材是否新颖、贴切？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-bvml5gu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-bvml5gu","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-66e6yht","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-66e6yht","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"结构与逻辑"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​：段落衔接是否自然？论证层次是否清晰？开头结尾是否有力？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-tz86mzt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-tz86mzt","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-hl83b08","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-hl83b08","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"语言表达"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​：是否有语病、错别字？修辞是否恰当？语言是否有文采/感染力？"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-dxcggsk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-dxcggsk","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-k9wetvu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-k9wetvu","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"书写与规范"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（若提供手写稿图片）：字迹是否工整？标点使用是否规范？卷面是否整洁？"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-uvg5uwn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-uvg5uwn","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-kryoa2p","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-kryoa2p","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-y0dybud","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-y0dybud","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"亮点与不足"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-z5v21zw","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-z5v21zw","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-dzcjonk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-dzcjonk","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-9ony8sk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-9ony8sk","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"列出2-3个具体亮点（引用原文句子，说明好在哪里）；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-tydn6r9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-tydn6r9","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-u9rhcea","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-u9rhcea","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"指出2-3个核心问题（避免空泛，如“论证不充分”需具体到“第三段论据与论点脱节，建议补充……”）。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-olsj481","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-olsj481","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-62ouss6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-62ouss6","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-yw2ocw0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-yw2ocw0","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"修改建议"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（分优先级）："}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-0wsj8x0","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-0wsj8x0","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-e7a37a5","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-e7a37a5","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-k0na02s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-k0na02s","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"紧急修改"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​：影响得分的关键问题（如偏题、严重语病），给出具体修改方向或示范句子；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-ldhnl9x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-ldhnl9x","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-16e5nz3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-16e5nz3","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"提升建议"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​：如何让作文从“合格”到“优秀”（如深化立意、优化结构、升级素材），提供1-2个可操作的技巧或素材推荐。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-h1xmjcf","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-h1xmjcf","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-gjescf2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-gjescf2","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-tmt7npz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-tmt7npz","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"参考评分"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​（满分60分）：给出预估分数，并简要说明扣分点（如“立意准确但素材陈旧，扣3分；结尾仓促，扣2分”）。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-shpi9mc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-shpi9mc","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"注意事项"}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-wer2yov","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-wer2yov","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-pqic11i","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-pqic11i","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-2s1mqqu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-2s1mqqu","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"避免空泛评价（如“语言优美”“结构清晰”），必须结合原文具体分析；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-4catycy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-4catycy","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-d7cq9nb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-d7cq9nb","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"修改建议需符合高中生认知水平，避免过度拔高或脱离实际；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-in3w9f7","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-in3w9f7","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-cg8ulv7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-cg8ulv7","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"鼓励性语言与批评性建议结合，保护学生写作积极性；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-qr7gpzo","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-qr7gpzo","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-ghi85nq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-ghi85nq","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"若作文存在明显偏题，优先解决立意问题，再谈其他维度。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-qs16hpy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-qs16hpy","updated":"20260610092648"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"作文内容"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"\n"}]},{"ID":"20260610092646-ngd6joq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092646-ngd6joq","updated":"20260610092646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"《“自由”二字的重量》"}]},{"ID":"20260610092646-r1p1ynv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092646-r1p1ynv","updated":"20260610092646"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"十二岁之前，“自由”是一只风筝。我站在田野上，看它越飞越高，幻想有一天能挣脱所有的线，飘向天涯海角。那时候的“自由”意味着不写作业、不上辅导班、不听妈妈的唠叨——意味着一切束缚的消失。  我像所有叛逆期的少年一样，对“自由”有着近乎偏执的渴望。初一那年暑假，我和父母大吵一架。原因很简单：他们给我报了一个数学强化班，而我想用那个暑假学吉他。我摔门而出，在小区的花园里坐了整整一个下午，满脑子都是“等我长大了，谁也管不了我，我要过自由的生活”。  后来，我如愿以偿地得到了一次“自由”的机会。初二寒假，父母临时出差一周，把我一个人留在家里。头两天我兴奋得像一条脱了缰的小马：半夜打游戏，中午才起床，一日三餐全是外卖，衣服扔在沙发上堆成小山。然而第三天，我开始感到一种空洞的不安。冰箱里什么都没有了，房间乱得下不去脚，我一个人坐在凌乱的客厅里，突然觉得这种“自由”不是飞翔，而是坠落——没有方向的坠落。  我第一次开始认真地思考：自由到底是什么？  高中的政治课给了我第一把钥匙。老师讲到卢梭的那句名言：“人是生而自由的，却无处不在枷锁之中。”他接着说了一句让我至今记忆犹新的话：“自由不是没有边界，自由是知道边界在哪里之后，依然有能力选择方向。”那一瞬间，我仿佛听到了脑海中什么东西“咔哒”一声的解锁声。  我开始重新审视生活中的那些“不自由”。每天的早自习让人困倦，但正是那些清晨的朗读，让我在语文考试中有了底气；每周的体育训练让人酸痛，但正是那些汗水，让我在运动会上冲过终点线时有了从容；甚至父母当年替我报的数学强化班——虽然我当时恨透了它——却实实在在地帮我打下了后来学好物理的基础。那些我曾经视为“束缚”的东西，其实都是通往更广阔自由的阶梯。  我渐渐理解了：真正的自由从来不是无拘无束，而是一种自律之后的游刃有余。一个钢琴家在台上自由地演奏，是因为他在台下经历了无数次机械枯燥的练习；一个作家自由地挥洒文字，是因为他在漫长的岁月里阅读了千百本书、写下了百万字的草稿。自由的根基是能力，而能力的根基是自律和积累。没有根基的自由，不过是放纵。  更深层的理解发生在高二。我读到康德的一句话：“自由不是你想做什么就做什么，而是你不想做什么就可以不做什么。”这让我明白，自由不仅是一种能力，更是一种清醒的自觉——它意味着你不被欲望裹挟、不被潮流驱赶、不被他人的评价左右，而是能够在喧嚣中保持独立判断，在压力面前做出忠于自我的选择。  如今，我不再把“自由”想象成一只断了线的风筝。断了线的风筝看似自由，其实只会被风摆布，最终跌落在某个无人知晓的角落。真正的自由，恰恰是那根线——它看似是束缚，却是方向，是支撑，是让你飞得更高、更远、更稳的力量。  从“挣脱一切”到“自律则自由”，这个词语在我心中的重量变了。它不再轻飘飘的，而是沉甸甸的——沉甸甸地落在每一个自我约束的清晨，每一次克服惰性的坚持里。这份重量，是我成长赠予我的最好礼物。"}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-3y4xecu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-3y4xecu","updated":"20260610092637"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"附加信息"}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-iukegko","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-iukegko","updated":"20260610092734"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-b2v1ytq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-b2v1ytq","updated":"20260610092734"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-7cdhozv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-7cdhozv","updated":"20260610092652"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作文题目/材料："}]},{"ID":"20260610092734-m48gvt6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092734-m48gvt6","updated":"20260610091710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"阅读下面的材料，根据要求写作。（60分）"}]},{"ID":"20260610092734-724ta49","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092734-724ta49","updated":"20260610091710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"词语是表达思想情感的载体，也是展现社会生活变化的窗口。当前，世界之变、时代之变、历史之变正以前所未有的方式展开。青年是常为新的，在你的成长过程中，你对哪一个词语的理解发生了变化？这变化有你成长的印记，对你有特殊的意义……"}]},{"ID":"20260610092734-zeceh0h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092734-zeceh0h","updated":"20260610091710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"以上材料引发了你怎样的联想和思考？请写一篇文章。"}]},{"ID":"20260610092734-03a5q6t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092734-03a5q6t","updated":"20260610091710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"要求：选准角度，确定立意，明确文体，自拟标题；不要套作，不得抄袭；不得泄露个人信息；不少于800字。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092544-6tf4y1r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-6tf4y1r","updated":"20260610092544"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260610092544-wyz2g3o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092544-wyz2g3o","updated":"20260610092604"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学生年级：高三"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260610092618-wna876e","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260610092618-wna876e","updated":"20260610092618"}}]}